title: BONUS EPISODE: J.I On Rap Game, Drake, Confidence + NY Rap
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro in the Morning sits down with J.I for a great conversation on his music style, confidence, not being seen as a reality show artist after his appearance on 'The Rap Game', Drake singing his music, what kind of artist he wants to be seen as, his favorite New York artists, and even his mom working for HOT 97 as an intern. Young & Restless Vol. 1 Baby Don is out now! #EbrointheMorning #HOT97 #JI
